Welcome to the course! As you learn about vector databases for RAG, discover how IBM watsonx.data supports vector workloads alongside structured data in a unified platform.

IBM watsonx.data is an open data lakehouse that lets teams manage all their data, including vector data for RAG applications, in one place.

What You Can Do with watsonx.data:

Run vector workloads alongside structured data

Build a unified data foundation for RAG applications

Query diverse data types from a single platform

Scale your data infrastructure for AI

